&lt;h3 data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;g-mm3x4p3i&quot; data-pm-slice=&quot;1 1 []&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY BOX NEEDS YOU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;We’re hiring an AI-native creator to help Box show up in the live AI conversation every day. This&amp;nbsp;is not a traditional social media manager role. You will be perpetually online in the AI&amp;nbsp;discourse—spotting what matters, forming smart takes, and publishing native content across&amp;nbsp;modern social channels. This role is intentionally ring-fenced from the normal campaign&amp;nbsp;machine so it doesn’t get deprioritized.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;The job is to help Box communicate and engage directly in-channel — on X, LinkedIn, and other&amp;nbsp;relevant platforms — rather than treating social only as a distribution layer for content that lives&amp;nbsp;somewhere else.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&quot;g-mm3x4p3l&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU’LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
