&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create strategic target account lists within a defined territory based on research&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Connect with potential clients through initial outreach via phone and email, actively seeking to understand their requirements&lt;/p&gt;
