&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY BOX NEEDS YOU&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data Engineering initiative inside box is expanding and this role will help build the data platform engineering features and capabilities of the cloud cost management platform.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
