&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Box needs you:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Box Extract team&lt;/strong&gt; is a core part of Box’s AI strategy, focused on transforming unstructured enterprise content (PDFs, contracts, invoices, forms, and more) into structured, actionable data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will lead a &lt;strong&gt;Warsaw-based engineering team&lt;/strong&gt; within the Box Extract organization. This team operates within the &lt;strong&gt;application layer&lt;/strong&gt;, responsible for turning advanced AI capabilities (OCR and LLM-based Extract Agents) into a scalable, customer-facing product.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
