&lt;li&gt;You possess at least 5 years of professional software development experience building full-stack web applications, preferably with JavaScript/TypeScript and Java&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Solid understanding of &lt;strong&gt;distributed systems and service-oriented architectures&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable operating across both &lt;strong&gt;backend and frontend concepts&lt;/strong&gt; (full-stack awareness)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong technical judgment — able to evaluate system design decisions, trade-offs, and engineering approaches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working in &lt;strong&gt;data-driven environments&lt;/strong&gt; (metrics such as velocity, predictability, delivery performance)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled at building and growing teams, supporting both senior and junior engineers&lt;/li&gt;
